"{\"uid\": \"buzzfeed.com-elizabethswaney-secrets-from-behind-the-scenes-at-the-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"The best of the internet, delivered straight to your inbox!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 59, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the internet\", \"from\": 12, \"to\": 24}, {\"ngram\": \"your inbox\", \"from\": 48, \"to\": 58}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If there is a heaven, it would be like the Olympic dining hall.\", \"from\": 61, \"to\": 124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a heaven\", \"from\": 73, \"to\": 81}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic dining hall\", \"from\": 100, \"to\": 123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"BuzzFeed Contributor Many Olympians refer to the \\\"Kit Day\\\" as one of the happiest days of their lives.\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 126, \"end\": 134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.971611793177358e-13, \"text\": \"BuzzFeed\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BuzzFeed\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many Olympians\", \"from\": 147, \"to\": 161}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Kit Day\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 183}, {\"ngram\": \"the happiest days\", \"from\": 195, \"to\": 212}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 227}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before flying out to the Olympic city, we receive many sweaters and jackets, lots of shirts, socks, towels, and even suitcases in our country's colors.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 381, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic city\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 267}, {\"ngram\": \"many sweaters\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"jackets\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 307, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"shirts\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 321}, {\"ngram\": \"socks\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 328}, {\"ngram\": \"towels\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"even suitcases\", \"from\": 342, \"to\": 356}, {\"ngram\": \"our country's colors\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 380}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Olympic Village, it then becomes easier to identify where everyone is from as everyone's dressed in flag colors with the name of their country in big letters on their chest or back.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 405}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 456}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"flag colors\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"the name\", \"from\": 507, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"their country\", \"from\": 519, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"big letters\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"their chest\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Receiving all the gear for free is a delight as over the years, the costs of winter sports clothing, along with other expenses like coaching, traveling, and more can add up!\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the gear\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"a delight\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"the costs\", \"from\": 636, \"to\": 645}, {\"ngram\": \"winter sports clothing\", \"from\": 649, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"other expenses\", \"from\": 684, \"to\": 698}, {\"ngram\": \"coaching\", \"from\": 704, \"to\": 712}, {\"ngram\": \"traveling\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kit Day is also where we meet many of our country's athletes from different sports for the first time.\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Kit Day\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"our country's athletes\", \"from\": 785, \"to\": 807}, {\"ngram\": \"different sports\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 829}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 848}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As I was the only freestyle skier for Hungary and mostly trained in Utah, before that day, I had not yet met the other Olympic team athletes from Hungary, including the alpine skiers, cross-country skiers, speed skaters, and figure skaters.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 1090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 888, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999567446985879, \"rank\": 4.312317755705005e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.999999999098236, \"rank\": 9.016776366012803e-10, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}, {\"begin\": 996, \"end\": 1003, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999567446985879, \"rank\": 4.312317755705005e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only freestyle skier\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"that day\", \"from\": 931, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"the other Olympic team athletes\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 990}, {\"ngram\": \"the alpine skiers\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"cross-country skiers\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"speed skaters\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"figure skaters\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even before the Olympics, and especially for the first week, you will be around your country's athletes and officials a lot.\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"the first week\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"your country's athletes\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1195}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I traveled from Hungary to Korea, with a long layover in Dubai, with 15 people I had just met.\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1233, \"end\": 1240, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999567446985879, \"rank\": 4.312317755705005e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 1244, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999997509521873, \"rank\": 2.489828333286974e-07, \"text\": \"Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 1274, \"end\": 1279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.230201113434177e-18, \"text\": \"Dubai\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dubai\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a long layover\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"15 people\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1295}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After landing in Seoul and then collecting our massive amounts of luggage (skiers need a lot of gear), we traveled three hours through the Korean countryside to Pyeongchang to get to the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 1312, \"to\": 1515, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1329, \"end\": 1334, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"score\": 0.9999999972687874, \"rank\": 2.731170746814518e-09, \"text\": \"Seoul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seoul\"}, {\"begin\": 1451, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9924529737724237, \"rank\": 0.007604416100745387, \"text\": \"Korean\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}, {\"begin\": 1473, \"end\": 1484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\", \"score\": 0.9999890172942395, \"rank\": 1.0982826154235218e-05, \"text\": \"Pyeongchang\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\"}, {\"begin\": 1499, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0200423645578847e-35, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our massive amounts\", \"from\": 1355, \"to\": 1374}, {\"ngram\": \"luggage\", \"from\": 1378, \"to\": 1385}, {\"ngram\": \"skiers\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1399, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"gear\", \"from\": 1408, \"to\": 1412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Olympic Village, you will enjoy meals together, stay in the Olympic dorms together, and enjoy other activities.\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"meals\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1560}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic dorms\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1596}, {\"ngram\": \"other activities\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The dining hall is everyone's favorite place.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The dining hall\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1651}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone's favorite place\", \"from\": 1655, \"to\": 1680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can talk to any coach or athlete, and nearly everyone is friendly.\", \"from\": 1682, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any coach\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"athlete\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly everyone\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can also eat whatever we want 24 hours a day and choose between 20+ dining stations.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 1769, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"24 hours\", \"from\": 1786, \"to\": 1794}, {\"ngram\": \"20+ dining stations\", \"from\": 1820, \"to\": 1839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic dining hall is the central meeting area at the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1917, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic dining hall\", \"from\": 1842, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"the central meeting area\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 1916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everyone is wearing their country jackets so it's easy to find and talk to people from all around the world.\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 2026, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"their country jackets\", \"from\": 1938, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2025}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes I would walk in and think, \\\"Hey, I want to have breakfast with the French team today\\\" or \\\"I am going to enjoy dessert with team Japan.\\\"\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2104, \"end\": 2110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9998047733841376, \"rank\": 0.00010100683548840467, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2160, \"end\": 2170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_at_the_1998_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.0494785345936636e-18, \"text\": \"team Japan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_at_the_1998_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_at_the_1998_Winter_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"breakfast\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"dessert\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearly everyone is relaxed and happy to enjoy the time between training and competitions.\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2262, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nearly everyone\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2188}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2219, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition to being with my fellow athletes from Hungary a lot, the dining hall was also a great place to catch up with old friends and meet new ones.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2314, \"end\": 2321, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999567446985879, \"rank\": 4.312317755705005e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"addition\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2275}, {\"ngram\": \"my fellow athletes\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2308}, {\"ngram\": \"the dining hall\", \"from\": 2329, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"a great place\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"old friends\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"new ones\", \"from\": 2406, \"to\": 2414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Before freestyle skiing, I also competed internationally in skeleton (headfirst down a bobsled track), so I loved catching up with my skeleton and bobsled friends around the world.\", \"from\": 2416, \"to\": 2596, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"freestyle skiing\", \"from\": 2423, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"skeleton\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"a bobsled track\", \"from\": 2501, \"to\": 2516}, {\"ngram\": \"my skeleton\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"bobsled friends\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2578}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2586, \"to\": 2595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the picture above, I am hanging out with my Monaco bobsled team friends.\", \"from\": 2597, \"to\": 2672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2644, \"end\": 2650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"score\": 0.9999999997062332, \"rank\": 2.390637068110289e-10, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the picture\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Upon arriving at the Olympic Village, each athlete is given a certain amount of pins from their country.\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"each athlete\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2724}, {\"ngram\": \"a certain amount\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2750}, {\"ngram\": \"pins\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2758}, {\"ngram\": \"their country\", \"from\": 2764, \"to\": 2777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can then trade the pins with other athletes and officials, or give them as gifts.\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2863, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pins\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2805}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 2811, \"to\": 2825}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2839}, {\"ngram\": \"gifts\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2862}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few returning Olympians planned ahead and made their personalized pins to give and trade away.\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A few returning Olympians\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2889}, {\"ngram\": \"their personalized pins\", \"from\": 2913, \"to\": 2936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Imagine the biggest tent you have seen in your life, and under it, thousands of Olympic athletes and officials are waiting a few hours to march.\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 3106, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest tent\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2986}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3013}, {\"ngram\": \"thousands\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3038}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic athletes\", \"from\": 3042, \"to\": 3058}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 3063, \"to\": 3072}, {\"ngram\": \"march\", \"from\": 3100, \"to\": 3105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To pass the time and burn off some energy, we all chat, exchange stories, and trade pins.\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3123}, {\"ngram\": \"some energy\", \"from\": 3137, \"to\": 3148}, {\"ngram\": \"exchange stories\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3179}, {\"ngram\": \"trade pins\", \"from\": 3185, \"to\": 3195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We can not stray too far away from our country, because we will need to get in line for the parade of nations.\", \"from\": 3197, \"to\": 3307, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our country\", \"from\": 3232, \"to\": 3243}, {\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 3276, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"the parade\", \"from\": 3285, \"to\": 3295}, {\"ngram\": \"nations\", \"from\": 3299, \"to\": 3306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once we do start going around the Olympic track that holds the ceremonies, people in the crowds are cheering, and it's all waves and smiles.\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic track\", \"from\": 3338, \"to\": 3355}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremonies\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3381}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3383, \"to\": 3389}, {\"ngram\": \"the crowds\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3403}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 3431, \"to\": 3436}, {\"ngram\": \"smiles\", \"from\": 3441, \"to\": 3447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's the moment many athletes have dreamt of for most of their lives.\", \"from\": 3449, \"to\": 3518, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3464}, {\"ngram\": \"many athletes\", \"from\": 3465, \"to\": 3478}, {\"ngram\": \"their lives\", \"from\": 3506, \"to\": 3517}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All countries parade in alphabetical order based on the host country's language.\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All countries\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3533}, {\"ngram\": \"alphabetical order\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3562}, {\"ngram\": \"the host country's language\", \"from\": 3572, \"to\": 3599}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since \\\"Hungary\\\" was toward the end of the Korean alphabet, we paraded right in front of the host country, Korea, so it was exciting to hear a lot of cheers.\", \"from\": 3601, \"to\": 3757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3608, \"end\": 3615, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999567446985879, \"rank\": 4.312317755705005e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}, {\"begin\": 3643, \"end\": 3658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Korean alphabet\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hangul\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 3635}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 3680, \"to\": 3685}, {\"ngram\": \"the host country\", \"from\": 3689, \"to\": 3705}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3741, \"to\": 3746}, {\"ngram\": \"cheers\", \"from\": 3750, \"to\": 3756}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the opening ceremonies, the athletes and officials from South and North Korea paraded together, so I thought it was cool to experience that historic moment next to me.\", \"from\": 3758, \"to\": 3932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3831, \"end\": 3842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9999999999986358, \"rank\": 1.3325604294430766e-12, \"text\": \"North Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/North_Korea\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 3765, \"to\": 3787}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 3789, \"to\": 3801}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3815}, {\"ngram\": \"South\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3826}, {\"ngram\": \"that historic moment\", \"from\": 3900, \"to\": 3920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympic ceremony itself is a spectacular show.\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 3984, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympic ceremony\", \"from\": 3934, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectacular show\", \"from\": 3965, \"to\": 3983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are drones, fireworks, dances, and excited athletes all around.\", \"from\": 3985, \"to\": 4054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drones\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4001}, {\"ngram\": \"fireworks\", \"from\": 4003, \"to\": 4012}, {\"ngram\": \"dances\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4020}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 4034, \"to\": 4042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus, it feels like all the television cameras in the world are watching.\", \"from\": 4055, \"to\": 4128, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the television cameras\", \"from\": 4075, \"to\": 4101}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 4105, \"to\": 4114}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We received the best blanket ever with pictures of all the Olympic sports.\", \"from\": 4130, \"to\": 4204, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the best blanket\", \"from\": 4142, \"to\": 4158}, {\"ngram\": \"pictures\", \"from\": 4169, \"to\": 4177}, {\"ngram\": \"all the Olympic sports\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Plus, we got stuffed animals and a new backpack.\", \"from\": 4205, \"to\": 4253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stuffed animals\", \"from\": 4218, \"to\": 4233}, {\"ngram\": \"a new backpack\", \"from\": 4238, \"to\": 4252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like being a kid again.\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4282, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a kid\", \"from\": 4270, \"to\": 4275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now at home, I hang my blanket on a wall to remind me of my Olympic days.\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4356, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 4290, \"to\": 4294}, {\"ngram\": \"my blanket\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4313}, {\"ngram\": \"a wall\", \"from\": 4317, \"to\": 4323}, {\"ngram\": \"my Olympic days\", \"from\": 4340, \"to\": 4355}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes also have roommates at the Olympic Village.\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Athletes\", \"from\": 4358, \"to\": 4366}, {\"ngram\": \"roommates\", \"from\": 4377, \"to\": 4386}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 4390, \"to\": 4409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With Hungary, we were in one of five or so towers, and had most of the floor to ourselves.\", \"from\": 4411, \"to\": 4501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4416, \"end\": 4423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9999567446985879, \"rank\": 4.312317755705005e-05, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"five or so towers\", \"from\": 4443, \"to\": 4460}, {\"ngram\": \"the floor\", \"from\": 4478, \"to\": 4487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the 2018 Winter Olympians, 2,292 Olympians competed for 259 medals.\", \"from\": 4503, \"to\": 4573, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 2018 Winter Olympians\", \"from\": 4506, \"to\": 4531}, {\"ngram\": \"2,292 Olympians\", \"from\": 4533, \"to\": 4548}, {\"ngram\": \"259 medals\", \"from\": 4562, \"to\": 4572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By comparison, 111,000 condoms were available at Pyeongchang.\", \"from\": 4574, \"to\": 4635, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4623, \"end\": 4634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\", \"score\": 0.9999890172942395, \"rank\": 1.0982826154235218e-05, \"text\": \"Pyeongchang\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pyeongchang_County\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"comparison\", \"from\": 4577, \"to\": 4587}, {\"ngram\": \"111,000 condoms\", \"from\": 4589, \"to\": 4604}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each Olympian and official receives a limited-edition Olympic phone.\", \"from\": 4637, \"to\": 4705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"official\", \"from\": 4655, \"to\": 4663}, {\"ngram\": \"a limited-edition Olympic phone\", \"from\": 4673, \"to\": 4704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only a few thousand are made at each Olympics.\", \"from\": 4706, \"to\": 4752, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"each Olympics\", \"from\": 4738, \"to\": 4751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The phone is helpful so we can communicate with our country officials and other athletes, and best of all, take photos.\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The phone\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4762}, {\"ngram\": \"our country officials\", \"from\": 4801, \"to\": 4822}, {\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 4827, \"to\": 4841}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 4865, \"to\": 4871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The photo-capturing quality was spectacular on these new phones.\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The photo-capturing quality\", \"from\": 4873, \"to\": 4900}, {\"ngram\": \"these new phones\", \"from\": 4920, \"to\": 4936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is actually a tradition at most Olympics, so the more Olympics someone competes at, the more phones they get!\", \"from\": 4938, \"to\": 5052, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a tradition\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 4966}, {\"ngram\": \"most Olympics\", \"from\": 4970, \"to\": 4983}, {\"ngram\": \"the more Olympics\", \"from\": 4988, \"to\": 5005}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 5006, \"to\": 5013}, {\"ngram\": \", the more phones\", \"from\": 5025, \"to\": 5042}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each athlete can take one coach to the Olympics, but I did not have one, so I gave my coach allocation to the Hungarian speed skating team.\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5164, \"end\": 5173, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9882858714563539, \"rank\": 0.011852890162127813, \"text\": \"Hungarian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Each athlete\", \"from\": 5054, \"to\": 5066}, {\"ngram\": \"one coach\", \"from\": 5076, \"to\": 5085}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 5089, \"to\": 5101}, {\"ngram\": \"my coach allocation\", \"from\": 5137, \"to\": 5156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My friends Nicholas Vienneau and Allen Blackwell, skeleton coaches, offered to coach and support me.\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5205, \"end\": 5213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicholas_II_of_Russia\", \"score\": 0.9937503088628714, \"rank\": 0.0046352458040053, \"text\": \"Nicholas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"htt