xt\": \"Nick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Jonas\"}, {\"begin\": 5339, \"end\": 5347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skeleton_at_the_2006_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.679140057635269, \"rank\": 0.47245026924281863, \"text\": \"skeleton\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skeleton_at_the_2006_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skeleton_at_the_2006_Winter_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's common for small nations (countries with one or few athletes in a sport) to share coaches both during the Olympics and World Cup circuit.\", \"from\": 5415, \"to\": 5557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"small nations\", \"from\": 5431, \"to\": 5444}, {\"ngram\": \"countries\", \"from\": 5446, \"to\": 5455}, {\"ngram\": \"one or few athletes\", \"from\": 5461, \"to\": 5480}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport\", \"from\": 5484, \"to\": 5491}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 5502, \"to\": 5509}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics and World Cup circuit\", \"from\": 5522, \"to\": 5556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic officials want to make sure athletes have everything they need at the Olympic Village, without having to venture to the outside world.\", \"from\": 5559, \"to\": 5701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic officials\", \"from\": 5559, \"to\": 5576}, {\"ngram\": \"sure athletes\", \"from\": 5590, \"to\": 5603}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 5609, \"to\": 5619}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 5633, \"to\": 5652}, {\"ngram\": \"the outside world\", \"from\": 5683, \"to\": 5700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The salons are particularly popular before the opening ceremonies, and also before any medals ceremonies because everyone wants to look their best.\", \"from\": 5702, \"to\": 5849, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The salons\", \"from\": 5702, \"to\": 5712}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremonies\", \"from\": 5745, \"to\": 5767}, {\"ngram\": \"any medals\", \"from\": 5785, \"to\": 5795}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 5815, \"to\": 5823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I got a haircut the day of the opening ceremony, and then came back to get my nails painted in the Olympic colors, which is pictured above.\", \"from\": 5850, \"to\": 5989, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a haircut\", \"from\": 5856, \"to\": 5865}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 5877, \"to\": 5897}, {\"ngram\": \"my nails\", \"from\": 5925, \"to\": 5933}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic colors\", \"from\": 5945, \"to\": 5963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe that the hair and nails were the only things that required payment at the Olympic Village, apart from the souvenir shop.\", \"from\": 5990, \"to\": 6120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hair\", \"from\": 6005, \"to\": 6013}, {\"ngram\": \"nails\", \"from\": 6018, \"to\": 6023}, {\"ngram\": \"the only things\", \"from\": 6029, \"to\": 6044}, {\"ngram\": \"payment\", \"from\": 6059, \"to\": 6066}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 6070, \"to\": 6089}, {\"ngram\": \"the souvenir shop\", \"from\": 6102, \"to\": 6119}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In the photo, I am holding a chocolate medal, one of the many treats that Olympians received at the Village.\", \"from\": 6121, \"to\": 6229, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the photo\", \"from\": 6124, \"to\": 6133}, {\"ngram\": \"a chocolate medal\", \"from\": 6148, \"to\": 6165}, {\"ngram\": \"the many treats\", \"from\": 6174, \"to\": 6189}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 6195, \"to\": 6204}, {\"ngram\": \"the Village\", \"from\": 6217, \"to\": 6228}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I heard that the dental services are particularly popular at the Olympic Village and to sign up early.\", \"from\": 6231, \"to\": 6333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dental services\", \"from\": 6244, \"to\": 6263}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Village\", \"from\": 6292, \"to\": 6311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not need any work, but was able to get a teeth cleaning.\", \"from\": 6334, \"to\": 6396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any work\", \"from\": 6349, \"to\": 6357}, {\"ngram\": \"a teeth cleaning\", \"from\": 6379, \"to\": 6395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the Olympic competition sites, regular and emergency medical care is also available.\", \"from\": 6397, \"to\": 6484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic competition sites\", \"from\": 6400, \"to\": 6429}, {\"ngram\": \"regular and emergency medical care\", \"from\": 6431, \"to\": 6465}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This helps Olympians stay all smiles!\", \"from\": 6485, \"to\": 6522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 6496, \"to\": 6505}, {\"ngram\": \"all smiles\", \"from\": 6511, \"to\": 6521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Here I am with fellow Olympic friends Pita (Tonga) and German (Mexico), both cross-country skiers.\", \"from\": 6523, \"to\": 6621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6561, \"end\": 6565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pita\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.49607323181409e-28, \"text\": \"Pita\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pita\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pita\"}, {\"begin\": 6567, \"end\": 6572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\", \"score\": 0.9999999951251084, \"rank\": 4.826505495386961e-09, \"text\": \"Tonga\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tonga\"}, {\"begin\": 6578, \"end\": 6584, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"score\": 0.9857770530255635, \"rank\": 0.014352914719796708, \"text\": \"German\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/German_language\", \"dbpedia